Reports

Class Report

  • java.lang.Object
    • Reports.Report
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SourceAnalysis, SourceReview

    public abstract class Report
extends java.lang.Object
    A Report consistents of a collection of Scans that the user wants to run on the given input file. To create a new report, make a subclass of whatever title, and in the default constructor instantiate scans with whatever scan objects desired. Then fill in the functionality for generateReport().
